{"tid":1892064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有無人可以留意下工聯會口罩利益輸送？","createTime":"2020-02-22T09:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T13:23:57.000Z","uid":3513,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f0b376d8c339136ae60bc0ad68778a3b8f2a3472","tid":1892064,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:45:40.000Z","msg":"#手動轉<br />\n<br />\n工聯會記者會説會成立11條口罩生產線，政府承諾資助每條生產線成立款項是<br />\n頭1條生產$3,000,000+以後10條 x $2,000,000=<br />\n總數$23,000,000<br />\n<br />\n政府日後向每條生產線保証每月採購2,000,000個口罩，政府初步承諾採購價每個$3，為期1年：<br />\n$3 x 2,000,000個  x 11條生產線 x 12個月=<br />\n總數$792,000,000<br />\n<br />\n工聯會總資助：$815,000,000<br />\n<br />\n文件披露懲教署出售每個口罩：$0.13<br />\n<br />\n初步估算工聯會1年淨袋$757,680,000=<br />\n($3 - $0.13) x 264,000,000個<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇，只送不賣有乜所謂呀，就算當你生產唔到咁多，打個5折，條數大家自己諗<br />\n<br />\n香港人水深火熱，重掛住利益輸送，而且重扮好人為香港人好，繼續愚民，邊有人咁可恥！？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Facebook 見到，請問我地尊貴嘅泛民議員有無留意到當中魔鬼細節？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"2a15dc0b0b44860e979ffbef71c69d050657d4a3","tid":1892064,"uid":324229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:46:07.000Z","msg":"屯門聽日(2月23日)有活動 求推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1892049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1892049</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b332b7555c0196cc6c74205bec963ee1797597d4","tid":1892064,"uid":3513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:46:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">假防疫 真輸送<br />\n賣港狗死全家</span>"},{"pid":"6d12deb8ccea75c0b4af6d79aab3f9d327e84d6c","tid":1892064,"uid":3513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:46:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">假防疫 真輸送<br />\n賣港狗死全家</span